text: Sally Carman-Duttine (born 9 May 1975) is an English actress. She is known for her roles as Kelly Maguire in the Channel 4 comedy-drama series Shameless (2005–2013), and Abi Franklin in the ITV soap opera Coronation Street (2017–present). Carman was born in Mexborough, South Yorkshire, the county of England. At 18, she attended the LAMDA drama school in London. She has also appeared in Doctors, Heartbeat, and Holby City. ==Other websites== * * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:English television actors Category:People from South Yorkshire
